---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
description: Complex tech. Simple explanations. Tutorials on AI, DevOps, and modern software engineering.
---

<div class="hero">
  <h1>TechAI Explained</h1>
  <p>Complex tech. Simple explanations. Deep-dive tutorials on AI agents, Kubernetes, reactive programming, and modern developer tools.</p>
</div>

<div class="section-header">
  <h2>📚 Latest Tutorials</h2>
</div>

<div class="card-grid">
  {%- for article in collections.articles -%}
  <div class="card">
    <span class="tag">{{ article.data.tags[0] if article.data.tags else 'Tutorial' }}</span>
    <h3><a href="{{ article.url | url }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a></h3>
    <p>{{ article.data.description }}</p>
    <div class="meta">{{ article.data.date | readableDate }} · {{ article.data.readTime or '8 min read' }}</div>
  </div>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>

<div class="section-header">
  <h2>🎥 Video Script Outlines</h2>
</div>

<div class="card-grid">
  {%- for script in collections.videoScripts -%}
  <div class="card">
    <span class="tag">Video Script</span>
    <h3><a href="{{ script.url | url }}">{{ script.data.title }}</a></h3>
    <p>{{ script.data.description }}</p>
    <div class="meta">{{ script.data.date | readableDate }}</div>
  </div>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
